  "structuredContent": {
    "content": "# 生物 Demo-Ready 冲刺 1 实现计划\n\n> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.\n\n**Goal:** 让生物学科知识树在浏览器中可视化呈现，并接通 answer_logs → BKT 数据管道，为 demo 做好基础。\n\n**Architecture:** 不新建任何子系统。将已有的 sync 脚本接入 app 启动、将已有的 `_update_adaptive_mastery` 接入 pipeline event handler、增强前端节点详情面板调用已有 API。\n\n**Tech Stack:** FastAPI (async lifespan) / SQLAlchemy 2.0 (async) / Vue 3 + AntV G6 / PostgreSQL\n\n**Design:** `docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-design.md`\n\n---\n\n## 文件结构\n\n| 操作 | 文件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py:23-148` | lifespan 增加 knowledge.db → PG 同步 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py` | on_exam_published 增加 adaptive mastery 更新 |\n| Modify | `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` | 增加 sync_da_kp_map 函数 |\n| Modify | `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue` | 增强详情面板（课标/教材/真题） |\n| Modify | `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js` | 增加 getNodeDetail API |\n| Create | `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py` | 节点详情聚合服务 |\n| Create | `tests/test_services_exam/test_knowledge_sync.py` | 同步测试 |\n| Create | `tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py` | pipeline 接通测试 |\n| Create | `tests/test_services_exam/test_node_detail.py` | 节点详情 API 测试 |\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 启动同步\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py:64-66` (lifespan, 在 create_all 之后添加)\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` (添加 sync_da_kp_map)\n- Create: `tests/test_services_exam/test_knowledge_sync.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 启动时 concept_graph_nodes 为空 → 触发全量同步\n- ✓ 启动时 concept_graph_nodes 已有数据 → 跳过（幂等）\n- ✓ knowledge.db 不存在 → 警告日志，不崩溃\n- ✓ sync_da_catalog 同步 156 DA 到 da_catalog_snapshot\n- ✓ sync_da_kp_map 从 DA concept_ids 写入 DaKnowledgePointMap\n- ✗ 同步失败后应用仍能启动（非致命）\n- ✗ 同步不应删除学校端自定义数据（当前无此场景，但验证 sync 只写骨架表）\n\n**边界条件:**\n- knowledge.db 文件不存在 → 期望: 警告日志，跳过同步，应用正常启动\n- knowledge.db 中 concepts 表为空 → 期望: 同步 0 行，不报错\n- 重复调用同步（应用重启）→ 期望: 幂等，数据一致\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 启动同步写入 concept_graph_nodes\n   - 入口: app lifespan 启动流程（通过 `sync_knowledge_graph_on_startup` 函数直接调用验证）\n   - 反例: 如果不调用 sync_to_postgres，concept_graph_nodes 保持 0 行——本测试验证同步后行数 > 0\n   - 边界: knowledge.db 不存在 / concepts 表为空 / 重复同步\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_knowledge_sync.py -v`\n\n2. sync_da_kp_map 写入 DaKnowledgePointMap\n   - 入口: `sync_da_kp_map(knowledge_db_path, db)` 直接调用\n   - 反例: 如果不从 DA concept_ids 提取映射，DaKnowledgePointMap 保持 0 行——本测试验证写入后行数 > 0\n   - 边界: DA 无 concept_ids / concept_id 不在 concept_graph_nodes 中\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_knowledge_sync.py::test_sync_da_kp_map -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 写 sync_da_kp_map 函数**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py` 末尾添加:\n\n```python\nasync def sync_da_kp_map(knowledge_db_path: str, db: \"AsyncSession\") -> int:\n    \"\"\"从 knowledge.db 同步 DA → 知识点映射到 DaKnowledgePointMap。\n\n    每个 DA 的 linked_concept_ids 展开为 (da_id, concept_id) 行。\n    \"\"\"\n    from sqlalchemy import select, delete\n    from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(knowledge_db_path)\n    try:\n        catalog = build_da_catalog_from_knowledge_db(conn)\n    finally:\n        conn.close()\n\n    # 全量替换\n    await db.execute(delete(DaKnowledgePointMap))\n\n    count = 0\n    for item in catalog:\n        for concept_id in (item.get(\"concept_ids\") or []):\n            db.add(DaKnowledgePointMap(\n                da_id=item[\"da_id\"],\n                knowledge_point_id=concept_id,\n                weight=1.0,\n            ))\n            count += 1\n\n    await db.commit()\n    return count\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 写启动同步函数**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` 的 lifespan 函数中，在 `logger.info(\"database tables created\")` 之后、`# Load knowledge base` 之前插入:\n\n```python\n    # Sync knowledge.db → PostgreSQL (concept graph + DA catalog + DA-KP map)\n    from pathlib import Path\n    knowledge_db_path = Path.home() / \"edu-knowledge-base\" / \"knowledge.db\"\n    if knowledge_db_path.exists():\n        async with async_session() as db:\n            from sqlalchemy import select, func\n            from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode\n            count = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))).scalar()\n            if count == 0:\n                from scripts.sync_concept_graph import read_knowledge_db, sync_to_postgres\n                nodes, edges = read_knowledge_db(str(knowledge_db_path))\n                await sync_to_postgres(db, nodes, edges)\n                logger.info(\"sync: knowledge graph → PG (%d nodes, %d edges)\", len(nodes), len(edges))\n\n                from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.sync import sync_da_catalog, sync_da_kp_map\n                da_count = await sync_da_catalog(str(knowledge_db_path), db)\n                kp_count = await sync_da_kp_map(str(knowledge_db_path), db)\n                logger.info(\"sync: DA catalog → PG (%d DAs, %d KP mappings)\", da_count, kp_count)\n            else:\n                logger.debug(\"sync: knowledge graph already populated (%d nodes), skipping\", count)\n    else:\n        logger.warning(\"sync: knowledge.db not found at %s, skipping\", knowledge_db_path)\n```\n\n注意: `scripts.sync_concept_graph` 需要能被 import。在 `scripts/` 目录添加 `__init__.py` 或改为绝对 import。更简洁的方案是把 `read_knowledge_db` 和 `sync_to_postgres` 移入 `knowledge_tree/` 模块。但为最小改动，直接 sys.path hack:\n\n改为在 app.py 中直接内联调用已有函数（sync_concept_graph.py 的函数是独立的，不依赖 app context），或更好的方案——将同步逻辑提取为 service 函数。\n\n**实际方案（最小改动）：** 在 lifespan 中直接调用 sync_concept_graph.py 中的纯函数：\n\n```python\n    # Sync knowledge.db → PostgreSQL (concept graph + DA catalog + DA-KP map)\n    from pathlib import Path\n    knowledge_db_path = Path.home() / \"edu-knowledge-base\" / \"knowledge.db\"\n    if knowledge_db_path.exists():\n        async with async_session() as db:\n            from sqlalchemy import func\n            from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode\n            count_result = await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))\n            node_count = count_result.scalar()\n            if node_count == 0:\n                import sqlite3 as _sqlite3\n                import re as _re\n                _MODULE_RE = _re.compile(r\"_M(\\d+)_\")\n                _conn = _sqlite3.connect(str(knowledge_db_path))\n                _conn.row_factory = _sqlite3.Row\n                _nodes = []\n                for row in _conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts\"):\n                    m = _MODULE_RE.search(row[\"id\"])\n                    _nodes.append({\n                        \"id\": row[\"id\"], \"name\": row[\"name\"],\n                        \"knowledge_level\": row[\"knowledge_level\"],\n                        \"primary_module\": f\"M{m.group(1)}\" if m else \"unknown\",\n                        \"description\": row[\"description\"],\n                    })\n                _edges = []\n                for row in _conn.execute(\"SELECT source_id, target_id, relation_type, strength, confidence FROM concept_relations\"):\n                    _edges.append({\n                        \"source_id\": row[\"source_id\"], \"target_id\": row[\"target_id\"],\n                        \"relation_type\": row[\"relation_type\"],\n                        \"strength\": row[\"strength\"] or 1.0, \"confidence\": row[\"confidence\"] or 1.0,\n                    })\n                _conn.close()\n                # 用已有 sync 函数写入\n                from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode as _N, ConceptGraphEdge as _E\n                import sqlalchemy as _sa\n                from datetime import datetime as _dt\n                _now = _dt.now()\n                await db.execute(_sa.delete(_E))\n                await db.execute(_sa.delete(_N))\n                for n in _nodes:\n                    db.add(_N(id=n[\"id\"], name=n[\"name\"], knowledge_level=n[\"knowledge_level\"],\n                              primary_module=n[\"primary_module\"], description=n[\"description\"], synced_at=_now))\n                await db.flush()\n                for e in _edges:\n                    db.add(_E(source_id=e[\"source_id\"], target_id=e[\"target_id\"], relation_type=e[\"relation_type\"],\n                              strength=e[\"strength\"], confidence=e[\"confidence\"], synced_at=_now))\n                await db.commit()\n                logger.info(\"sync: knowledge graph → PG (%d nodes, %d edges)\", len(_nodes), len(_edges))\n\n                from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.sync import sync_da_catalog, sync_da_kp_map\n                da_count = await sync_da_catalog(str(knowledge_db_path), db)\n                kp_count = await sync_da_kp_map(str(knowledge_db_path), db)\n                logger.info(\"sync: DA catalog → PG (%d DAs, %d KP mappings)\", da_count, kp_count)\n            else:\n                logger.debug(\"sync: knowledge graph already populated (%d nodes), skipping\", node_count)\n    else:\n        logger.warning(\"sync: knowledge.db not found at %s, skipping\", knowledge_db_path)\n```\n\n**但这太冗长且重复 sync_concept_graph.py 的代码。** 更好的方案：\n\n- [ ] **Step 2 (修订): 将 sync 逻辑提取为可 import 的 service 函数**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py` 创建:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 同步服务（app 启动时调用）。\"\"\"\nimport logging\nimport re\nimport sqlite3\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nimport sqlalchemy as sa\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import AsyncSession\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\nDEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB = Path.home() / \"edu-knowledge-base\" / \"knowledge.db\"\n_MODULE_RE = re.compile(r\"_M(\\d+)_\")\n\n\ndef _read_knowledge_db(db_path: str) -> tuple[list[dict], list[dict]]:\n    \"\"\"读取 knowledge.db 的 concepts 和 concept_relations。\"\"\"\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(db_path)\n    conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n    nodes = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts\"):\n        m = _MODULE_RE.search(row[\"id\"])\n        nodes.append({\n            \"id\": row[\"id\"], \"name\": row[\"name\"],\n            \"knowledge_level\": row[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            \"primary_module\": f\"M{m.group(1)}\" if m else \"unknown\",\n            \"description\": row[\"description\"],\n        })\n    edges = []\n    for row in conn.execute(\n        \"SELECT source_id, target_id, relation_type, strength, confidence FROM concept_relations\"\n    ):\n        edges.append({\n            \"source_id\": row[\"source_id\"], \"target_id\": row[\"target_id\"],\n            \"relation_type\": row[\"relation_type\"],\n            \"strength\": row[\"strength\"] or 1.0, \"confidence\": row[\"confidence\"] or 1.0,\n        })\n    conn.close()\n    return nodes, edges\n\n\nasync def _sync_graph(db: AsyncSession, nodes: list[dict], edges: list[dict]) -> None:\n    \"\"\"全量替换 PostgreSQL 中的概念图谱。\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphEdge))\n    await db.execute(sa.delete(ConceptGraphNode))\n    for n in nodes:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphNode(\n            id=n[\"id\"], name=n[\"name\"], knowledge_level=n[\"knowledge_level\"],\n            primary_module=n[\"primary_module\"], description=n[\"description\"], synced_at=now,\n        ))\n    await db.flush()\n    for e in edges:\n        db.add(ConceptGraphEdge(\n            source_id=e[\"source_id\"], target_id=e[\"target_id\"],\n            relation_type=e[\"relation_type\"], strength=e[\"strength\"],\n            confidence=e[\"confidence\"], synced_at=now,\n        ))\n    await db.commit()\n\n\nasync def sync_knowledge_on_startup(db: AsyncSession, knowledge_db_path: str | None = None) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"启动时同步 knowledge.db → PostgreSQL（幂等：已有数据则跳过）。\n\n    同步内容:\n    1. concept_graph_nodes + edges（知识图谱结构）\n    2. da_catalog_snapshot（DA 目录）\n    3. da_knowledge_point_map（DA → 概念映射）\n\n    Returns: {\"status\": \"synced\"|\"skipped\"|\"not_found\", \"nodes\": int, \"edges\": int, \"das\": int, \"kp_map\": int}\n    \"\"\"\n    path = Path(knowledge_db_path) if knowledge_db_path else DEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB\n    if not path.exists():\n        logger.warning(\"sync: knowledge.db not found at %s\", path)\n        return {\"status\": \"not_found\"}\n\n    count_result = await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))\n    existing = count_result.scalar() or 0\n    if existing > 0:\n        logger.debug(\"sync: knowledge graph already populated (%d nodes), skipping\", existing)\n        return {\"status\": \"skipped\", \"nodes\": existing}\n\n    # 1. 图谱同步\n    nodes, edges = _read_knowledge_db(str(path))\n    await _sync_graph(db, nodes, edges)\n    logger.info(\"sync: knowledge graph → PG (%d nodes, %d edges)\", len(nodes), len(edges))\n\n    # 2. DA 目录 + DA-KP 映射\n    from edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.sync import sync_da_catalog, sync_da_kp_map\n    da_count = await sync_da_catalog(str(path), db)\n    kp_count = await sync_da_kp_map(str(path), db)\n    logger.info(\"sync: DA catalog → PG (%d DAs, %d KP mappings)\", da_count, kp_count)\n\n    return {\"status\": \"synced\", \"nodes\": len(nodes), \"edges\": len(edges), \"das\": da_count, \"kp_map\": kp_count}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 在 app lifespan 中调用 sync**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` 的 lifespan 中，`logger.info(\"database tables created\")` 之后添加:\n\n```python\n    # Sync knowledge.db → PostgreSQL (idempotent)\n    async with async_session() as db:\n        from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n        sync_result = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db)\n        if sync_result[\"status\"] == \"synced\":\n            logger.info(\n                \"sync: knowledge.db → PG complete (%d nodes, %d edges, %d DAs, %d KP maps)\",\n                sync_result[\"nodes\"], sync_result[\"edges\"], sync_result[\"das\"], sync_result[\"kp_map\"],\n            )\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_services_exam/test_knowledge_sync.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"knowledge.db → PostgreSQL 同步测试。\"\"\"\nimport pytest\nfrom unittest.mock import patch, MagicMock\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\n\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaCatalogSnapshot, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_populates_nodes_and_edges(db_session):\n    \"\"\"同步后 concept_graph_nodes 和 edges 应有数据。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    result = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session)\n\n    if result[\"status\"] == \"not_found\":\n        pytest.skip(\"knowledge.db not available in test environment\")\n\n    assert result[\"status\"] == \"synced\"\n    assert result[\"nodes\"] > 0\n    assert result[\"edges\"] > 0\n\n    count = (await db_session.execute(\n        select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode)\n    )).scalar()\n    assert count == result[\"nodes\"]\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_is_idempotent(db_session):\n    \"\"\"第二次调用应跳过同步。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    r1 = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session)\n    if r1[\"status\"] == \"not_found\":\n        pytest.skip(\"knowledge.db not available\")\n\n    r2 = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session)\n    assert r2[\"status\"] == \"skipped\"\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_missing_db_returns_not_found(db_session):\n    \"\"\"knowledge.db 不存在时返回 not_found，不崩溃。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup\n    result = await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session, knowledge_db_path=\"/nonexistent/path.db\")\n    assert result[\"status\"] == \"not_found\"\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_sync_da_kp_map(db_session):\n    \"\"\"sync_da_kp_map 应写入 DA → knowledge_point 映射。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.sync_service import sync_knowledge_on_startup, DEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB\n    if not DEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB.exists():\n        pytest.skip(\"knowledge.db not available\")\n\n    await sync_knowledge_on_startup(db_session)\n    count = (await db_session.execute(\n        select(func.count()).select_from(DaKnowledgePointMap)\n    )).scalar()\n    assert count > 0\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_knowledge_sync.py -v`\nExpected: 至少 test_sync_missing_db_returns_not_found PASS。其他测试依赖 knowledge.db 是否存在。\n\n- [ ] **Step 6: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/sync_service.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/modules/adaptive/sync.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/api/app.py \\\n        tests/test_services_exam/test_knowledge_sync.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: knowledge.db → PG 启动同步（concept graph + DA catalog + DA-KP map）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: 接通 answer_logs → BKT 管道\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py:11-33`\n- Create: `tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ exam.published 事件触发 _update_adaptive_mastery\n- ✓ 幂等：同一考试重复触发不重复写入（AnswerLog 唯一约束）\n- ✓ 现有 update_knowledge_mastery 和 update_error_patterns 不受影响\n- ✗ _update_adaptive_mastery 失败不应阻塞其他流水线步骤\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 考试无题目 → 期望: _update_adaptive_mastery 返回 0，不报错\n- 学生缺考（is_absent=True）→ 期望: 跳过该学生\n- 同一考试重复发布 → 期望: AnswerLog 幂等，不重复插入\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. pipeline 事件触发 adaptive mastery 更新\n   - 入口: `on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": ..., \"school_id\": ...})` 事件处理\n   - 反例: 不调用 _update_adaptive_mastery 则 answer_logs 保持 0 行——本测试验证调用后有数据\n   - 边界: 无题目考试 / 缺考学生 / 重复触发\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 修改 pipeline/__init__.py**\n\n将 `on_exam_published` 函数修改为:\n\n```python\n@event_bus.on(\"exam.published\")\nasync def on_exam_published(payload: dict) -> None:\n    \"\"\"成绩发布后触发完整流水线（知识点掌握度 + 错误模式 + DA 自适应）。\"\"\"\n    exam_id = payload.get(\"exam_id\")\n    school_id = payload.get(\"school_id\")\n    if not exam_id or not school_id:\n        logger.warning(\"on_exam_published: missing exam_id or school_id\")\n        return\n\n    from edu_cloud.database import async_session\n    from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service import (\n        update_knowledge_mastery, update_error_patterns, _update_adaptive_mastery,\n    )\n\n    async with async_session() as db:\n        mastery = await update_knowledge_mastery(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n        patterns = await update_error_patterns(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n        adaptive = await _update_adaptive_mastery(db, exam_id=exam_id, school_id=school_id)\n        await db.commit()\n    logger.info(\n        \"on_exam_published: exam=%s, mastery=%d, patterns=%d, adaptive=%d\",\n        exam_id, mastery, patterns, adaptive,\n    )\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"验证 exam.published 事件触发 adaptive mastery 更新。\"\"\"\nimport pytest\nfrom unittest.mock import AsyncMock, patch\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_on_exam_published_calls_adaptive_mastery():\n    \"\"\"on_exam_published 应调用 _update_adaptive_mastery。\"\"\"\n    with patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service._update_adaptive_mastery\", new_callable=AsyncMock) as mock_adaptive, \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service.update_knowledge_mastery\", new_callable=AsyncMock, return_value=0), \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.modules.pipeline.service.update_error_patterns\", new_callable=AsyncMock, return_value=0), \\\n         patch(\"edu_cloud.database.async_session\") as mock_session_factory:\n\n        mock_adaptive.return_value = 10\n\n        mock_db = AsyncMock()\n        mock_ctx = AsyncMock()\n        mock_ctx.__aenter__ = AsyncMock(return_value=mock_db)\n        mock_ctx.__aexit__ = AsyncMock(return_value=False)\n        mock_session_factory.return_value = mock_ctx\n\n        from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline import on_exam_published\n        await on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": \"test-exam\", \"school_id\": \"test-school\"})\n\n        mock_adaptive.assert_called_once_with(mock_db, exam_id=\"test-exam\", school_id=\"test-school\")\n\n\n@pytest.mark.asyncio\nasync def test_on_exam_published_missing_payload():\n    \"\"\"缺少 exam_id 或 school_id 时应直接返回。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.pipeline import on_exam_published\n    # 不应抛异常\n    await on_exam_published({})\n    await on_exam_published({\"exam_id\": \"x\"})\n    await on_exam_published({\"school_id\": \"x\"})\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py -v`\nExpected: PASS\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py \\\n        tests/test_services_exam/test_adaptive_pipeline.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: 接通 answer_logs → BKT 管道（exam.published → _update_adaptive_mastery）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: 节点详情聚合 API\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py`\n- Modify: `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` (添加 GET /graph/{node_id}/detail)\n- Create: `tests/test_services_exam/test_node_detail.py`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 返回课标、教材锚点、关联 DA、典型真题（全部从 knowledge.db 查）\n- ✓ 有学情时返回班级掌握率\n- ✓ knowledge.db 不可用时优雅降级（返回部分数据）\n- ✗ 节点 ID 不存在 → 404\n\n**边界条件:**\n- 节点 ID 不存在 → 期望: HTTP 404\n- knowledge.db 不可用 → 期望: 返回 PG 中已有数据，knowledge.db 字段为空列表\n- 节点无关联 DA → 期望: da_list 为空列表，不报错\n\n**测试契约:**\n1. 节点详情 API 返回结构化数据\n   - 入口: `GET /api/v1/knowledge-tree/graph/{node_id}/detail`\n   - 反例: 不查 knowledge.db 则 curriculum/textbook/questions 全为空——本测试验证有数据时字段非空\n   - 边界: 不存在的 node_id / knowledge.db 不可用\n   - 回归: N/A\n   - 命令: `python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_node_detail.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 创建 detail_service.py**\n\n`src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"节点详情聚合服务 — 从 knowledge.db 查询课标/教材/真题。\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport logging\nimport sqlite3\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\nDEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB = Path.home() / \"edu-knowledge-base\" / \"knowledge.db\"\n\n\ndef get_node_detail(node_id: str, knowledge_db_path: str | None = None) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"查询概念节点的详细信息（同步，从 knowledge.db 直接读取）。\n\n    Returns: {\n        concept: {id, name, level, module, description},\n        curriculum: [{requirement_id, content}],\n        textbook: [{section_title, chapter, book}],\n        das: [{da_id, name, observable_behaviors}],\n        questions: {near: [...], mid: [...], far: [...]},\n    }\n    \"\"\"\n    path = Path(knowledge_db_path) if knowledge_db_path else DEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB\n    if not path.exists():\n        return {\"concept\": {\"id\": node_id}, \"curriculum\": [], \"textbook\": [], \"das\": [], \"questions\": {}}\n\n    conn = sqlite3.connect(str(path))\n    conn.row_factory = sqlite3.Row\n\n    result: dict = {\"concept\": {\"id\": node_id}, \"curriculum\": [], \"textbook\": [], \"das\": [], \"questions\": {}}\n\n    # 1. 概念基本信息\n    row = conn.execute(\"SELECT id, name, knowledge_level, description FROM concepts WHERE id = ?\", (node_id,)).fetchone()\n    if row:\n        result[\"concept\"] = dict(row)\n\n    # 2. 关联 DA\n    das = conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        SELECT id, name, observable_behaviors, common_cause_families\n        FROM diagnostic_attributes\n        WHERE json_extract(linked_concept_ids, '$') LIKE ?\n    \"\"\", (f'%{node_id}%',)).fetchall()\n    result[\"das\"] = []\n    for da in das:\n        linked = json.loads(da[\"observable_behaviors\"]) if da[\"observable_behaviors\"] else []\n        result[\"das\"].append({\n            \"da_id\": da[\"id\"], \"name\": da[\"name\"],\n            \"observable_behaviors\": linked,\n        })\n\n    # 3. 课标要求（通过 DA → seed_req_da_map → curriculum_requirements）\n    da_ids = [d[\"da_id\"] for d in result[\"das\"]]\n    if da_ids:\n        placeholders = \",\".join(\"?\" * len(da_ids))\n        reqs = conn.execute(f\"\"\"\n            SELECT DISTINCT cr.id, cr.content\n            FROM curriculum_requirements cr\n            JOIN seed_req_da_map srdm ON srdm.requirement_id = cr.id\n            WHERE srdm.da_id IN ({placeholders})\n        \"\"\", da_ids).fetchall()\n        result[\"curriculum\"] = [{\"requirement_id\": r[\"id\"], \"content\": r[\"content\"]} for r in reqs]\n\n    # 4. 教材定位（通过概念名在 content_blocks 中搜索）\n    if row:\n        concept_name = row[\"name\"]\n        textbook_rows = conn.execute(\"\"\"\n            SELECT s.title AS section_title, d.title AS book\n            FROM content_blocks cb\n            JOIN sections s ON cb.section_id = s.id\n            JOIN documents d ON s.document_id = d.id\n            WHERE cb.content LIKE ? AND d.doc_type = 'textbook'\n            LIMIT 5\n        \"\"\", (f'%{concept_name}%',)).fetchall()\n        result[\"textbook\"] = [{\"section_title\": r[\"section_title\"], \"book\": r[\"book\"]} for r in textbook_rows]\n\n    # 5. 典型真题（通过 Q-Matrix DA 映射，按 transfer_band 分组，每组 3 题）\n    if da_ids:\n        for band in (\"near\", \"mid\", \"far\"):\n            items = conn.execute(f\"\"\"\n                SELECT DISTINCT ai.id, ai.stem, ai.answer, ai.question_type\n                FROM q_matrix qm\n                JOIN assessment_items ai ON qm.item_id = ai.id\n                WHERE qm.attribute_id IN ({placeholders})\n                  AND qm.transfer_band = ?\n                LIMIT 3\n            \"\"\", [*da_ids, band]).fetchall()\n            result[\"questions\"][band] = [\n                {\"id\": i[\"id\"], \"stem\": i[\"stem\"][:200], \"answer\": i[\"answer\"], \"type\": i[\"question_type\"]}\n                for i in items\n            ]\n\n    conn.close()\n    return result\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 添加路由**\n\n在 `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` 添加:\n\n```python\n@router.get(\"/graph/{node_id}/detail\")\nasync def get_node_detail_endpoint(\n    node_id: str,\n    db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db),\n    current: dict = Depends(get_current_user),\n):\n    \"\"\"获取概念节点的详细信息（课标/教材/DA/真题）。\"\"\"\n    require_permission(current, \"VIEW_KNOWLEDGE_TREE\")\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode\n    from sqlalchemy import select\n    node = (await db.execute(select(ConceptGraphNode).where(ConceptGraphNode.id == node_id))).scalar_one_or_none()\n    if not node:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=404, detail=\"Node not found\")\n\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    detail = get_node_detail(node_id)\n    return detail\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 写测试**\n\n`tests/test_services_exam/test_node_detail.py`:\n\n```python\n\"\"\"节点详情服务测试。\"\"\"\nimport pytest\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_missing_db():\n    \"\"\"knowledge.db 不存在时返回空结构。\"\"\"\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    result = get_node_detail(\"FAKE_NODE\", knowledge_db_path=\"/nonexistent.db\")\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"id\"] == \"FAKE_NODE\"\n    assert result[\"curriculum\"] == []\n    assert result[\"das\"] == []\n    assert result[\"questions\"] == {}\n\n\ndef test_node_detail_real_data():\n    \"\"\"knowledge.db 存在时返回实际数据。\"\"\"\n    db_path = Path.home() / \"edu-knowledge-base\" / \"knowledge.db\"\n    if not db_path.exists():\n        pytest.skip(\"knowledge.db not available\")\n\n    from edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.detail_service import get_node_detail\n    # 用一个已知的 M1 概念\n    result = get_node_detail(\"BIO_SR_CP_M1_CELL_MEMBRANE\", knowledge_db_path=str(db_path))\n    assert result[\"concept\"][\"name\"] is not None\n    assert len(result[\"das\"]) > 0  # 该概念应有关联 DA\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 运行测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest tests/test_services_exam/test_node_detail.py -v`\nExpected: test_node_detail_missing_db PASS; test_node_detail_real_data PASS if knowledge.db exists\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/detail_service.py \\\n        src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py \\\n        tests/test_services_exam/test_node_detail.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: 节点详情聚合 API（课标/教材/DA/真题，从 knowledge.db 查询）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: 前端节点详情面板增强\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue`\n- Modify: `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js`\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 点击节点 → 调用 /graph/{node_id}/detail → 渲染课标/教材/DA/真题\n- ✓ 数据加载中显示 loading 状态\n- ✓ API 失败时优雅降级（显示已有的基础信息）\n- ✗ 真题 stem 超长时截断显示\n\n**边界条件:**\n- API 返回空列表 → 期望: 显示\"暂无数据\"占位\n- 网络错误 → 期望: 显示错误提示，不崩溃\n- 快速切换节点 → 期望: 取消前一次请求，显示最新节点数据\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 添加 API 函数**\n\n在 `frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js` 添加:\n\n```javascript\nexport function getNodeDetail(nodeId) {\n  return client.get(`/knowledge-tree/graph/${nodeId}/detail`)\n}\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 增强 NodeDetailDrawer.vue**\n\n在 NodeDetailDrawer.vue 中，添加数据获取和 Tab 面板渲染。核心变更:\n\n1. 在 `<script setup>` 中添加 detail 数据获取:\n```javascript\nimport { ref, watch } from 'vue'\nimport { getNodeDetail } from '../../api/knowledgeTree'\n\nconst props = defineProps({ node: Object, visible: Boolean })\nconst detail = ref(null)\nconst loading = ref(false)\n\nwatch(() => props.node?.id, async (nodeId) => {\n  if (!nodeId) return\n  loading.value = true\n  detail.value = null\n  try {\n    const { data } = await getNodeDetail(nodeId)\n    detail.value = data\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.warn('Failed to load node detail:', e)\n  } finally {\n    loading.value = false\n  }\n})\n```\n\n2. 在模板中添加 NTabs 面板（概要 / 课标 / 教材 / DA / 真题）:\n```html\n<n-tabs type=\"line\" v-if=\"detail\">\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"curriculum\" tab=\"课标要求\">\n    <div v-for=\"req in detail.curriculum\" :key=\"req.requirement_id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      {{ req.content }}\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.curriculum.length\" description=\"暂无课标数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"textbook\" tab=\"教材定位\">\n    <div v-for=\"tb in detail.textbook\" :key=\"tb.section_title\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      <strong>{{ tb.book }}</strong> — {{ tb.section_title }}\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.textbook.length\" description=\"暂无教材数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"das\" tab=\"诊断属性\">\n    <div v-for=\"da in detail.das\" :key=\"da.da_id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n      <strong>{{ da.name }}</strong>\n      <ul><li v-for=\"b in da.observable_behaviors\" :key=\"b\">{{ b }}</li></ul>\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!detail.das.length\" description=\"暂无 DA 数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n  <n-tab-pane name=\"questions\" tab=\"典型真题\">\n    <div v-for=\"band in ['near', 'mid', 'far']\" :key=\"band\">\n      <h4>{{ {near:'基础',mid:'中等',far:'拓展'}[band] }}</h4>\n      <div v-for=\"q in (detail.questions[band] || [])\" :key=\"q.id\" class=\"detail-item\">\n        <p>{{ q.stem }}</p>\n        <p class=\"answer\">答案: {{ q.answer }}</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <n-empty v-if=\"!Object.keys(detail.questions).length\" description=\"暂无真题数据\" />\n  </n-tab-pane>\n</n-tabs>\n<n-spin v-else-if=\"loading\" />\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 运行前端测试**\n\nRun: `cd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend && npx vitest run`\nExpected: 现有测试全部 PASS（新增组件变更不应破坏现有测试）\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/NodeDetailDrawer.vue \\\n        frontend/src/api/knowledgeTree.js\ngit commit -m \"feat: 知识树节点详情面板（课标/教材/DA/真题 Tab 展示）\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: 端到端验证\n\n**Files:** 无新建文件\n\n**审查清单:**\n- ✓ 后端启动后 concept_graph_nodes 有 108+ 行\n- ✓ concept_graph_edges 有 335 行\n- ✓ da_catalog_snapshot 有 156 行\n- ✓ da_knowledge_point_map 有数据\n- ✓ 前端知识树页面渲染出节点\n- ✓ 点击节点显示详情面板\n\n- [ ] **Step 1: 启动后端验证数据同步**\n\n```bash\n# 在 WSL 中启动后端\ncd /mnt/c/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud\npython -m uvicorn edu_cloud.api.app:create_app --factory --host 0.0.0.0 --port 9000\n```\n\n检查启动日志中应出现:\n```\nsync: knowledge graph → PG (1233 nodes, 335 edges)\nsync: DA catalog → PG (156 DAs, xxx KP mappings)\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 2: 验证 PostgreSQL 数据**\n\n```bash\n# 连接数据库验证\npython -c \"\nimport asyncio\nfrom edu_cloud.database import async_session\nfrom sqlalchemy import select, func\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.knowledge_tree.models import ConceptGraphNode, ConceptGraphEdge\nfrom edu_cloud.modules.adaptive.models import DaCatalogSnapshot, DaKnowledgePointMap\n\nasync def check():\n    async with async_session() as db:\n        nodes = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphNode))).scalar()\n        edges = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(ConceptGraphEdge))).scalar()\n        das = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaCatalogSnapshot))).scalar()\n        kp = (await db.execute(select(func.count()).select_from(DaKnowledgePointMap))).scalar()\n        print(f'Nodes: {nodes}, Edges: {edges}, DAs: {das}, KP maps: {kp}')\n        assert nodes >= 108, f'Expected >=108 nodes, got {nodes}'\n        assert edges >= 335, f'Expected >=335 edges, got {edges}'\n        assert das >= 156, f'Expected >=156 DAs, got {das}'\n        assert kp > 0, f'Expected >0 KP maps, got {kp}'\n        print('All checks passed!')\n\nasyncio.run(check())\n\"\n```\n\n- [ ] **Step 3: 验证前端知识树渲染**\n\n```bash\n# 启动前端\ncd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend\npython ~/.claude/scripts/serve.py \"C:/Program Files/nodejs/npm.cmd\" run dev\n```\n\n打开 http://localhost:5273 → 登录(admin/123456) → 知识树页面 → 验证:\n1. 图谱渲染出节点和边\n2. 按模块筛选正常\n3. 点击节点显示详情面板（课标/教材/DA/真题 Tab）\n\n- [ ] **Step 4: 运行全量测试确认无回归**\n\n```bash\ncd C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud && python -m pytest --tb=short -q\n```\n\nExpected: 1582+ tests PASS，无 FAIL\n\n- [ ] **Step 5: Commit（如有修正）**\n\n```bash\ngit add -u\ngit commit -m \"fix: 端到端验证修正\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Contract Pack\n\n### invariants\n\n1. **知识图谱数据完整性**: sync 后 concept_graph_nodes 行数 ≥ knowledge.db concepts 行数\n   - verification: `test_sync_populates_nodes_and_edges` (existing_test)\n2. **同步幂等性**: 多次调用 sync_knowledge_on_startup 不重复插入\n   - verification: `test_sync_is_idempotent` (existing_test)\n3. **pipeline 不中断**: 新增 adaptive mastery 步骤不影响 update_knowledge_mastery 和 update_error_patterns\n   - verification: `test_on_exam_published_calls_adaptive_mastery` (existing_test)\n\n### counter_examples\n\n1. **sync 删除学校自定义数据**: 如果学校端编辑了 concept_graph_nodes（通过 edit API），sync 全量替换会丢失编辑\n   - tests_that_still_pass: edit 测试（已有）不会在 sync 后运行\n   - mitigation: sync 仅在 node_count==0 时触发，已有数据不会被覆盖\n\n2. **DA 映射链断裂**: 如果 DaKnowledgePointMap 中的 knowledge_point_id 不在 concept_graph_nodes 中\n   - tests_that_still_pass: resolve_da_ids 返回空列表\n   - mitigation: sync_da_kp_map 在 sync_graph 之后运行，concept_ids 来自同一 knowledge.db\n\n### risk_modules\n\n- `src/edu_cloud/api/app.py` (lifespan) — 启动流程变更\n- `src/edu_cloud/modules/pipeline/__init__.py` — 事件处理链变更\n- `src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py` — 新增路由\n\n### test_debt\n\n- 前端 NodeDetailDrawer 变更无自动化测试（Vitest 不覆盖 API 集成）\n  - 理由: 前端组件的 API 集成测试需要 mock 服务端，当前项目前端测试主要覆盖纯逻辑组件\n  - deadline: 冲刺 2 结束前补充 Vitest mock 测试\n"
